email-notifier microservice notifies users via email.

## Configuration:
Expected configuration file located at /config/application.properties.  This file must have some
or all of the following properties specified

# Place application.properties in mountable location and start the instance similar to below.

docker run --network=host --rm --name email-notifier -it -p 9091:8080 -v /data/email-notifier/configuration/:/config/ email-notifier:latest

# Service config
server.port=8080

#Logging configuration
logging.level.root=INFO
logging.level.cms.sre=INFO

emailnotifier.smtpHost=localhost
emailnotifier.smtpPort=25
emailnotifier.addressHost=default.com
emailnotifier.defaultSender=no-reply@default.com

